{"tid":1529172,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不問蒼生問鬼神，三元九運（要贏既話請參考）","createTime":"2019-09-01T16:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T04:16:13.000Z","uid":43288,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"698ee6e96eedcad2501515a73c6444634d1172ba","tid":1529172,"uid":43288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:30:07.000Z","msg":"去到呢一刻希望唔好覺得呢D係迷信，任何方法可以贏我地都要做！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">謀事在人，成事在天</span></span>。  <br />\n<br />\n大家有時間聽下，呢個節目卜左三支卦（包括示威者、政府、香港）教大家點去贏呢個局勢 我會係呢到講一下示威者卦既分析（卜卦有效時間為三個月同半年間）<br />\n<br />\n好消息係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢支係好卦</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LFvZ9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LFvZ9p.jpg&h=0d6d4272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\npart A<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L0QGpXyECro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL0QGpXyECro&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=d18822ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L0QGpXyECro</a><br />\n<br />\npart B<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Inp03fnOYXE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DInp03fnOYXE&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=ef3d231a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Inp03fnOYXE</a><br />\n<br />\npart C<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=npLhXZrSoxg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnpLhXZrSoxg&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=d82953ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=npLhXZrSoxg</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係我聽到，再分析<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">重點：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.1所有事都要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">出師有名</span></span>！ （每次都希望大家一齊諗下有咩objective！每次都要諗個好主題同背後行動目標。）  <br />\n<br />\n1.2主題：「反送中#metoo集會」、「守護香港反警黑集會」、「831反恐集會」、「美國領事請愿集會」諗好一個好名，吸引更多和理非同外媒更加關注。 <br />\n<br />\n 1.3背後行動目標：大家企係到唔走做咩？想比傳媒有咩畫面？想對家出醜或受傷？覆桌？ 我以近期為例：較成功既818，展現和理非冇人被拉，對家完全冇位插，外媒都大肆報導；第二係824，雖然個日有手足爆眼同有人被捕，最少我地最拆左燈柱發現有後門系統；最差係825，被捕人數眾多，為得晚上反黑個一下。 <br />\n<br />\n 2.要有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">紀律</span></span> （我都知大家都好紀律，但更加要堅持，緊守岡位，唔好自亂陣腳我地已經有三個月經驗，知道最基本應做咩同唔應該咩，唔好比情緒主導） <br />\n<br />\n 3.有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">小人作梗</span></span> （鬼可以唔哂捉，但要知。民間記者會可以將所有主流認為既暴力行為交返比佢地！）  <br />\n<br />\n4.最重要既一項係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搵更有經驗既人</span></span>做領導。反則以我地呢個形勢，只會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">帶屍回歸</span></span>。 （但可能變成我地認為既大台，同時我地可以搵咩人？前民運人士？泛民？銀髮族？外國勢力？大律師？內地維權人士？呢層大家可以brainstorm下）<br />\n<br />\n4.1如果情怳好嚴進的話，請退一退。以家我地打緊仗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有進有退係兵家常事</span></span>，唔代表我地係失敗，交個波比有經驗人士！（例如比佢地搞遊行、集會、領事請愿、聲名、記者會）<br />\n<br />\n卦中提及到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今年將會有三次大事發生</span></span>！8月31日？    9月8日？   10月1日？冇講好與壞，希望大家留意。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">利申：小弟學佛聽道，雖知現在係共業，但都唔可以任人宰割！</span>"},{"pid":"2dd91bc1a7ca76eab4bdc947f05e846e6738bb63","tid":1529172,"uid":219564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:30:30.000Z","msg":"建議9月8日百萬人大遊行，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案，宣揚攬炒精神﹗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1510235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1510235</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6246a32d4a8d9a87dff8fb367291ded9f6fad423","tid":1529172,"uid":43288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"297f1d32ff147d77a7156ae2f68fb028ed26785f","tid":1529172,"uid":43288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:32:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3605a6